{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#10199: The component introduced by defineAsyncComponent is bound to the component and SFC Playground cannot run",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:23:12.916356+00:00",
  "text": "The component introduced by defineAsyncComponent is bound to the component and SFC Playground cannot run\n\n### Vue version\n\nv3.4.13\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nClick to reproduce [SFC Playground](https://play.vuejs.org/#)\r\nLocal running projects can run, Unable to run in SFC Playground \r\n![image](https://github.com/vuejs/core/assets/29425637/1fa327cc-c40f-445d-97aa-cd80007c7fba)\r\n\n\n### What is expected?\n\nCan run on SFC Playground\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nLocal running projects can run, Unable to run in SFC Playground \r\n![image](https://github.com/vuejs/core/assets/29425637/1fa327cc-c40f-445d-97aa-cd80007c7fba)\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "scope: playground"
  ],
